    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not about a counselor or a \"new path.\" that's just more work. more stress. i'm just so tired of the fighting and the constant fear of everything breaking. it feels like the universe is telling me i'm done. like i've reached the end of my rope and there's nothing left to grab onto. i'm just sitting here in the dark and it feels so much easier than trying to fix it.",
