      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't feel like it's \"not permanent\" though. it feels permanent. like the dark is just where i belong now. i keep thinking about how much quiet there would be if i just stopped everything. no more debt, no more shame, no more trying to pretend everything is okay when it's clearly not. it just seems like such a logical way to finally get some peace.",
